.TP
.BR \-\-options
Display all available command-line options
.TP
.BR \-\-debug
Enable debug mode with verbose output and command tracing (set -x)
.TP
.BR \-\-raw
Disable colorized output for plain text display
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B readme-2-post README.md post.md
Convert README.md to post.md
.TP
.B readme-2-post ./README.md
Convert and output to stdout
